c: 57
v: 13
t: "Pazuva iro vanyengedzi, varume nevakadzi, vachati kune avo vanotenda: “Timirirei! Tibetserekane kubva muchaedza chenyu!” Zvichanzi: “Dzokerai kushure kwenyu! Motsvaga chiedza!” Saka mudhuri une gonhi uchaiswa pakati pavo. Mukati muchange muine tsitsi, uye panze pawo pachange paine murango"